com.here.android.mpa.search

Class AutoSuggestPlace

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.search.AutoSuggest
      • com.here.android.mpa.search.AutoSuggestPlace

  • public class AutoSuggestPlace
extends AutoSuggest
    Represents an AutoSuggestPlace which contains information about a suggested Place.

    Note: detailed Place information is retrieved by way of the PlaceRequest returned from a call to the getPlaceDetailsRequest() method.

      • getBoundingBox

        public final GeoBoundingBox getBoundingBox()
        Gets the GeoBoundingBox describing a range of coordinates that correspond to the Place. Typically, bounding boxes are associated with places such as cities and countries.

        Note: bounding box information for a Place is optional, so a call to this method could return null.

        Returns:
        The GeoBoundingBox containing the Place (could be null)
